nk":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9PY","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":38522,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/12\/14\/salat-dignity\/","url_meta":{"origin":37818,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Salah: Prayer with humility, dignity, tranquility","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 14, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Muttalib reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cPrayer is offered two cycles at a time, a sitting testimony offered after each two cycles, that you humbly express need, with calm and dignity, and you raise your hands, saying: O Allah! O Allah! Whoever has not done\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25295,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/10\/22\/qiblah-salat-east-west\/","url_meta":{"origin":37818,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Qiblah: Prayer direction between two cardinal directions","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 22, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhatever is between east and west is the direction of prayer.\u201d Al-Tirmidhi said, \"It has been narrated from more than one of the companions of the Prophet, that what is between east and west is the direction of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15104,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/16\/walk-in-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":37818,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Salah: When walking to prayer, you are in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 16, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen the prayer is established, do not come to it running, but rather come to it walking. You must be calm, for you may pray it if you reach it in time. If you miss anything\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31757,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/03\/no-salat-asr-fajr-exceptions\/","url_meta":{"origin":37818,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salat: No voluntary prayer after \u2018Asr and Fajr, with exceptions","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, only prayed two cycles after the afternoon prayer because some property came to him, which occupied him from performing two cycles after the noon prayer. The Prophet prayed them after the afternoon prayer and he did not repeat it.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3961,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/01\/oversleeps-misses-forgets-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":37818,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Prayer: If someone oversleeps and misses prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 1, 2012","format":fa